Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:11.39,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Earth... Our blue, shining planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:17.29,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But Earth was never as peaceful as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:42.40,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If your dad ever dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.24,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:58.62,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.66,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Today, the first semester of my \Nsecond year of high school ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:09.21,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, summer break starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:17.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he quit the track team \Nto focus on his studies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:21.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Has he picked up any bad habits, \Nlike staying out late?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.41,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:27.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think there has to be some reason \Nwhy his grades have fallen so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.36,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've been playing in my room a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:36.30,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I was playing video games and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:41.03,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,But I spent more time reading \Nbooks, or on the internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.28,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,studying things that interested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:49.80,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't what they call "studying." \NIt's just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.80,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:56.23,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You have to start thinking about \Nwhat you'll do after high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.04,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any dreams or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:01.22,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Like following in your father's footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His father has nothing to do with his future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.10,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:15.40,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's something wrong \Nwith me, with the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.62,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,But, most likely, I'm only imagining it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:25.10,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm actually just trying to escape\N because I don't feel like studying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.83,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,the stuff they assign at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.13,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Daichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:36.91,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Kagawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.20,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.59,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,My family owns this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.53,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to come unannounced?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.60,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. My parents aren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.89,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.27,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Daichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.08,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I found him at the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.52,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sasaki and Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Daichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.67,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's invite Daichi-kun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, I'm sure Ayano will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Having lots of people will be more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.55,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.89,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going to a villa in Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.18,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You guys want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,A villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Will the old guy with the glasses complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.61,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't really your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:44.53,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi's father was an astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.74,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,"Was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.82,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.92,Default - italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This footage was taken by a local resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.09,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Rainbow Seen \NOver Minamitane
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.38,Default - italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This strange rainbow circle appeared \Nin the sky over the town
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:04.05,Default - italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,of Minamitane in Tanegashima for \Nabout five minutes, before disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.13,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.50,Default - italics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the national weather \Nforecast for tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.17,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.15,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I won't be going to the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.61,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.46,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,No Entry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.22,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.14,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.89,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,What is that blue thing on your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:48.39,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.24,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Blue Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.89,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,My dad gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.82,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,It's very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:56.84,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.02,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,What is a "dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.02,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,When was it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:08.30,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,that I began to hate the wind \Nthat blows in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.46,Default,Pink,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Albion Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Moco-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:28.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, you'll finally be able to \Npilot that Machine Goodfellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.93,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, so I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I'll be able to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:37.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You two are always together. \NWhat, are you an item?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.93,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then on our next day off, let's go on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I might take you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.79,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,It's harvest season.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.18,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found the last person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.84,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,and the Machine Goodfellow will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.09,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,We are the planetary gears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We reveal the dream of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:28.24,Default,Ak,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His temperature is down to \Nthirty-eight degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:56.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But his singularity is causing \Nthis phenomenon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then he was an avatar, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.27,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see the news yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.66,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,That rainbow circle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.27,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.34,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Weird weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.74,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.24,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(363,1)}Strange Rainbow Seen \NOver Minamitane
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.96,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that rainbow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.71,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.22,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.20,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:35.22,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,if you can do something that surprises me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:38.72,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.86,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.61,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,if I jumped from a spot higher than that fence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.65,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,No way... You can't jump from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.67,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.24,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.53,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.14,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,I promised, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:06.01,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you can surprise me, I'll return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:14.68,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.75,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,The wind on this island feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.07,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Daichi Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.80,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I am Teppei Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:35.64,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Daichi... Want me to show \Nyou one last amazing thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.24,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.45,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,That really is amazing, Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.04,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're strange, Daichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.80,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.52,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Tanegashima \NThe Island of Romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from Toshiaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He said your letter didn't say where you'd gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but he thought you'd probably come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're done here, head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.47,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.10,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Did my father really die in an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.27,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing NEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.47,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.06,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,appears to be an AEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.98,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Star Emblem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.48,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning emergency launch sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.20,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Taiyou! Think of Daichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.07,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, this is the only thing \Nwe can use as an Impacter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.80,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsutomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:19.01,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hope means believing that the future \Nwill be better than today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:23.43,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And real hope can only come \Nfrom the choices you make!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.68,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.53,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.90,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:36.61,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutomu, look after Earth for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.00,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:55.90,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... He was a wonderful captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.97,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.77,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.90,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If your dad ever dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.32,Default - flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He'll die with a smile on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:27.74,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since my dad died in space, \NI've never returned to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.71,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I think the last time I saw Teppei, and her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.03,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,was three months before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.63,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.76,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.28,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can get in through this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.43,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,But it's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.22,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there another way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.48,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.79,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei said he'd show me something \Namazing, so I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.45,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, everything went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.63,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,And then, beyond the darkness, I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.84,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,She never wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.37,Default - flashback,?,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:56.25,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.86,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.08,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Daichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.43,Default - flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:16.23,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:20.62,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.40,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.50,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:41.09,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,it's kind of scary to come here alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:49.37,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Am I completely lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.90,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I really should know better than to follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.03,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,This is Setsuna's capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.97,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you realize this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.95,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,but with this much, you can't stay out there long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.82,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.12,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.63,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,High-density libido charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.46,Default,Am,0000,0000,0000,,Abreaction standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.92,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I was my real self!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seeing an Entangle Gate and an AEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency message from Governor \NYomatsuri, on the {\i1}Tenkaidou{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:20.31,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Our observation satellites have detected \Nan Approaching-Earth Object.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.52,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It matches the Kiltgang's manifestation pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,AEO's manifestation area is \Nwithin defensive zone 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Lambda sector, distance 360,000 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.99,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Defensive zone 1 center Impacter deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.99,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Russian base's Markovs have already \Nactivated their intercept systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I got on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.68,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how far down does this go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,The power went out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.99,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.51,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is that thing heading toward Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:40.93,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.26,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,If it reaches Earth, something terrible will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:45.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Mode change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:54.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:01.95,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.13,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.23,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.86,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that thing you're holding is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.70,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.92,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.79,Default,?,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:53.34,Default - flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... He was a wonderful captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.14,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'm a captain or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.68,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to stop that thing falling from space!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All Markovs are lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiltgang is heading straight for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Current distance 32,000 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Speed is 50 meters per second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Any other Impacters within the Lambda sector?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:22.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Governor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Expansion sequence has activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Constructing satellite chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tidal Combine Gate creation is now possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Course set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Initiating countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:39.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:42.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,1.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:49.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Gate, Marine Gate, Road Gate... \NCoordinates are all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:51.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Alonzo has begun the Earth Engine \Nemergency startup sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:55.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Pegasus rocket's launch pad is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency scramble fuel cartridge loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:11.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus rocket taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine's energy is charging!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's Orgone energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Teppei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What about Livlaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei Arashi isn't in the medical center.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Livlaster Blossom located in the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Pegasus rocket is purging Earth Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:34.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Relative vector adjustment... \NDelta RV, Sigma 3.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,2.6.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,0.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,First expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tidal attractor functioning normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Delta RV is within threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Combine robustness at maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Second expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing Orgone connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All systems are go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Final expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Engine series has expanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then someone who can use \Nthe Livlaster has appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:13.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To those of us in the Ark Faction, \Nthis is a serious concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:18.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We must not give those in the \NIntercept Faction any cause to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:20.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:24.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Especially those at Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:31.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:35.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth Engine Impacter...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My first battle in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:22.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm getting my butt kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:25.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a mysterious flight director saves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:28.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:31.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A passing magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:34.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 2 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:36.07,Default - margin,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Name of the Gun Is Livlaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:36.08,Title2,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Name of the Gun Is Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.39,0:24:38.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, expand!
